1158
01:13:03,520 --> 01:13:07,200
 A danas, naravno, znače nešto potpuno negativno.

1159
01:13:07,200 --> 01:13:09,540
 I oni će tvoj izbor svjesni tumačiti,

1160
01:13:09,540 --> 01:13:11,000
 pa ti si poludila ovako nakon.

1161
01:13:11,080 --> 01:13:12,580
 ti možeš završiti pet fakulteta,

1162
01:13:12,580 --> 01:13:13,560
 ali si prlupala.

1163
01:13:13,560 --> 01:13:15,900
 Možeš raditi posao 15 puta,

1164
01:13:15,900 --> 01:13:16,720
