1179
01:14:01,680 --> 01:14:05,340
 da polaznična pozicija treba biti,

1180
01:14:05,340 --> 01:14:10,380
 da mi zapravo to vjerojatno uopće ne razumijemo

1181
01:14:10,380 --> 01:14:12,440
 ili razumijemo krivo.

1182
01:14:12,440 --> 01:14:16,240
 I naš pogled na Mariju je,

1183
01:14:16,240 --> 01:14:20,280
 to je sad kažem, ne mušto sve i nedorečeno

1184
01:14:20,280 --> 01:14:22,960
 i nestručno, ali meni se čini da je naš pogled,

1185
01:14:22,960 --> 01:14:25,220
 taj vjerski pogled na Mariju,

1186
01:14:26,360 --> 01:14:29,260
 slab u smislu,

1187
01:14:29,260 --> 01:14:31,080
 mi, evo ovako,

1188
01:14:31,080 --> 01:14:33,240
 nedovoljno ozbiljno svačamo

1189
01:14:33,240 --> 01:14:35,620
 njezinu...

1190
01:14:35,620 --> 01:14:38,020
 Možda smo joj reducirali samo na zagovornicu.

1191
01:14:38,020 --> 01:14:38,900
 Recimo, da.

1192
01:14:38,900 --> 01:14:41,000
 Nedovoljno ozbiljno svačamo

1193
01:14:41,000 --> 01:14:43,760
