1235
01:16:01,480 --> 01:16:04,540
 I tamo mi se čini da to radimo...

1236
01:16:04,540 --> 01:16:05,440
 Evo, ako ću sad reći,

1237
01:16:05,440 --> 01:16:06,380
 nadam se da neće nikog

1238
01:16:06,380 --> 01:16:07,600
