1269
01:17:02,220 --> 01:17:03,120
 kontemplirat

1270
01:17:03,120 --> 01:17:04,340
 i u krajnjoj liniji

1271
01:17:04,340 --> 01:17:04,860
 pitat

1272
01:17:04,860 --> 01:17:06,460
