1273
01:17:06,460 --> 01:17:08,160
 Dobro, crkva je to

1274
01:17:08,160 --> 01:17:09,840
 kroz niz dokumenta

1275
01:17:09,840 --> 01:17:10,900
 i pape su se o tome

1276
01:17:10,900 --> 01:17:11,440
 izjašnjavale

1277
01:17:11,440 --> 01:17:12,480
 jako fino objasnila

1278
01:17:12,480 --> 01:17:12,880
 vupće

1279
01:17:12,880 --> 01:17:14,700
 Marijinu ulogu

1280
01:17:14,700 --> 01:17:15,720
 i sve što ona predstavlja

1281
01:17:15,720 --> 01:17:16,160
 i

1282
